headline: Should You Reconsider AutoZone After Its 21.5% Rally and Expansion News?
summary: Wondering if AutoZone is a bargain or overpriced? You are not alone, as questions about its true value pop up any time a stock enjoys the kind of performance AutoZone has shown recently. The stock has climbed 3.1% in the past week and is up a staggering 21.5% year-to-date, suggesting growing confidence in its prospects or a shift in how investors perceive its risk and reward. Analysts and market watchers have been buzzing about AutoZone’s expansion moves, including continued store openings...
